  "id": "RAW_f73a77f1",
  "title": "为什么大多数 AI 产品都失败了？来自 OpenAI 和 Google 的 50+ 次实战经验丨 Lenny's Podcast",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk5MDkxNDU4Nw==&mid=2247485175&idx=1&sn=966eb9fb0061eb822de22f77e5c1cd6d",
  "date": "2026-01-12 13:40:00",
  "author": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "siteName": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5c0cca48&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FaubJvugmGm3AF4mgkW2EsPrwCa3Y4q9uNkWn5BGTdDqjwf2pqFL3K5oeaneBc7UicCwwxTUicrM4H0GCwWqBfhxg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h1 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">我们每天为你更新硅谷最新的 AI 创业与科技播客总结，让你与前沿保持同频。全文约 4500 字，如果你现在没有时间，试试听文章播客</span></span><a class=\"weapp_image_link js_weapp_entry\" data-miniprogram-type=\"image\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wxa4c5894e8895e7d1\" data-miniprogram-path=\"pages/player/player?podcastId=019bb265-4f6f-77e4-a86e-931b582913b4&amp;openWithin=true\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"晚点再听LaterCast\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"#小程序://晚点再听/KABhN8MfkzUtkNk\" data-miniprogram-imageurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/aubJvugmGm3MsjfMGwQrW2XnYZL7jFzPEsY0zs7ZE3ibia8qyHxNv6PhXphfbSicwmRPa2JSibzZEO5Kvh1iaXtEsvA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"140\" data-backw=\"578\" data-ratio=\"0.24188790560471976\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-w=\"1017\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f807faf8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FaubJvugmGm3MsjfMGwQrW2XnYZL7jFzPEsY0zs7ZE3ibia8qyHxNv6PhXphfbSicwmRPa2JSibzZEO5Kvh1iaXtEsvA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></a></h1>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">“很多团队是从「模型能做什么」开始的，而不是从「用户真正需要什么」开始。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">“在真实的落地场景中，可靠性比纯粹的智能水平更重要。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">“构建是廉价的，但设计和判断是昂贵的。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">本期内容来自 Aishwaria Srinivasan 和 Kiriti Reddy 的分享。他们</span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">曾帮助 OpenAI、Google、Amazon 和 Databricks 等公司构建并发布了 50 多款企业级 AI 产品。基于这些经验，她们总结出了一套构建和扩展成功 AI 产品的最佳实践。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 产品与传统软件的关键差异</span></span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">许多团队失败的根本原因，在于他们试图用管理确定性系统的逻辑来管理概率性系统。Aishwaria 和 Kiriti 指出，AI 产品与传统软件之间存在两个根本性的区别，这直接决定了构建方式的差异。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">第一个区别是：双向的“非确定性”。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在传统软件时代，以 Booking.com 为例，用户的意图被严格限制在按钮和表单里：你想订房，你选择日期，点击搜索。这是一个高度确定性的工作流：意图 -&gt; 明确的行动 -&gt; 预期的结果。但在 AI 产品中，这一层被自然语言界面取代了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“你现在面对的是一个输入、输出和处理过程都不完全可控的系统。你不知道用户会怎么说，也不知道 LLM 会怎么回。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种非确定性体现在两个维度：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">1.&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">输入端：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">用户可以用一千种不同的方式表达同一个意图，或者表达出你从未预设过的意图。这与点击固定的按钮完全不同。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">2.&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">输出端：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">LLM 是概率模型，它对提示词极其敏感，本质上是一个黑盒。即使输入相同，输出也可能不同。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">这就意味着，你无法像编写传统代码那样，通过穷举所有边缘情况来保证稳定性。你正在试图用非确定性的技术，去达成企业所要求的确定性结果。这是 AI 产品构建中最核心的矛盾。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">第二个区别是：代理权与控制权的权衡。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是目前业界讨论较少、但风险极大的领域。每个人都想构建“自主代理（Autonomous Agents）”，希望 AI 能自动完成工作。但这里存在一个零和博弈：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">每当你赋予 AI 更多的代理权（做决策的能力），你就必须放弃相应程度的控制权。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你让 AI 自动处理退款，你就失去了对这笔资金流出的直接控制。如果你让 AI 自动回复客户，你就失去了对品牌声誉的绝对把控。因此，构建 AI 产品的核心挑战，不再是“技术上能不能实现”，而是“组织上敢不敢放权”。这取决于 AI 是否已经通过表现赢得了足够的“信任”。而在产品设计的初期，过度追求高代理权往往是灾难的开始。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\">做成 AI 产品和做不成的公司，差别在哪</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在目睹了 50 多个 AI 项目的起落后，Aishwaria 和 Kiriti 总结出了清晰的成败模式。这不仅是技术问题，更多是组织和文化问题。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">成功者的模式：领导者亲自下场“重建直觉”</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">最成功的公司，往往有一位“痴迷”的 CEO 或领导者。Rackspace 的 CEO 是一个典型的例子，他每天早上 4 点到 6 点的时间块是雷打不动的“Catching up with AI”。这不仅仅是阅读新闻，而是亲自上手、甚至写代码、与专家讨论。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么要这么做？因为过去 15 年积累的管理直觉在 AI 时代可能已经失效了。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">领导者必须变得脆弱，承认自己是房间里最笨的人，并通过亲手实践来重建对“AI 能做什么、不能做什么”的直觉。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;只有顶层有了正确的认知，才不会对团队提出“三天上线全自动客服”这种不切实际的要求，才能做出正确的资源分配决策。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，成功的文化是“增强”而非“替代”。在很多失败的案例中，领域专家拒绝配合，因为他们害怕教会了 AI 就会丢掉饭碗。而成功的企业会明确传达：AI 是为了让你 10 倍于现在的产出，是为了消除繁琐工作，而非消除你。这种心理安全感是获取高质量领域知识的前提。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">挣扎者的反模式：迷信“一键生成”与忽视数据债务</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">最典型的失败路径是购买所谓的“一键式 AI 代理（One-click Agent）”。如果有人试图卖给你一个开箱即用、能立刻接管你复杂业务流程的 AI，那大概率是营销谎言。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“即使拥有最好的模型，要在企业内部构建一个能产生显著 ROI 的系统，通常也需要 4 到 6 个月的脏活累活。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">失败的公司往往痴迷于模型本身（是选 GPT-4 还是 Claude 3.5？），而忽略了对自己工作流和数据的深度理解。企业的数据通常是一团糟，有着混乱的分类学和废弃的字段。例如，在零售企业的数据库中，可能存在多层级且互相冲突的商品分类（“鞋子”下有“男鞋”，但平级目录里又有“男性用品”）。AI 不会自动理清这些，必须有人去处理这些“技术债务”。忽视数据治理，直接上大模型，得到的结果只能是垃圾进，垃圾出。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\">3. 一套来自实战的迭代式 AI 构建方法</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了解决上述问题，他们开发了一套名为 CCCD（Continuous Calibration, Continuous Development，持续校准，持续开发）的框架。这可以被视为 AI 时代的 CI/CD，但更强调对非确定性行为的校准。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心理念非常务实：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">不要试图一步登天构建 V3（全自动代理）。从 V1（高控制、低代理）开始，逐步释放自主权。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这不仅是为了降低风险，更是为了收集数据。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">让我们以“客户支持代理”为例，拆解这个过程：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">V1：路由助手（高控制，低代理）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">目标：仅仅让 AI 负责把工单分类并转发给正确的部门，不直接回复客户。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">价值：这听起来很简单，但在企业复杂的分类体系下，这并不容易。通过这一步，你可以清理数据标签，理解 AI 对你业务分类的理解能力。即使 AI 错了，人工也能轻松纠正，风险极低。这一步帮助你验证了基础设施和数据质量。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">V2：Copilot 建议者（中控制，中代理）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">目标：AI 生成回复草稿，但这草稿是给“人类客服”看的，而不是直接发给客户。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">价值：人类客服可以选择发送、编辑或通过草稿。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">最关键的是，你要记录人类的每一次“编辑”和“拒绝”。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这些数据就是金矿——它们是免费的错误分析，告诉你 AI 哪里做得不对，哪里还需要改进。你在建立一个数据飞轮，利用人类专家的纠正来微调模型或优化 Prompt。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">V3：全自动代理（低控制，高代理）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">目标：AI 直接面对客户解决问题，甚至处理退款。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">前提：只有当你从 V2 收集了足够的数据，证明 AI 的准确率已经达标，且你会对意外情况的发生概率有足够把握时，才迈出这一步。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种阶梯式的构建方式，不仅能防止灾难性的错误，还能迫使团队专注于“问题本身”，而不是被技术的复杂性淹没。它强迫你在扩大规模之前，先解决信任和质量问题。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\">4. 为什么信任与可靠性，才是 AI 产品最核心却最常被忽视的因素</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">伯克利的一项最新研究显示，75% 的企业表示，阻碍他们将 AI 投入生产的最大障碍是“可靠性”。这并不是一个技术细节，而是决定产品生死的关键。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是一个被严重低估的驱动因素。在消费级产品（如 ChatGPT）中，如果 AI 偶尔胡说八道，用户可能会觉得有趣或者这就是个玩具。但在企业级应用中，一次严重的幻觉可能导致法律诉讼或巨额损失。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">加拿大航空的案例就是一个警钟：他们的聊天机器人“发明”了一项退款政策，承诺给乘客退款，而这实际上违反了航空公司的规定。最终，法院判决航空公司必须遵守机器人承诺的条款。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是为什么“信任”是 AI 产品的核心货币。如果你一开始就推出了一个不可靠的全自动系统，用户一旦被“咬”过一次，重建信任的成本将是天文数字。CCCD 框架的本质，就是通过逐步释放控制权，来缓慢但稳固地建立这种信任。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">不要通过牺牲用户体验来换取 AI 的学习，要在保护用户体验的同时进行后台学习。</span></strong></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">5. 评估为什么不是灵丹妙药，以及人们最常犯的评估误区</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你在 2024 年下半年混迹于 AI 圈，你会发现“Evals”这个词无处不在。每个人都在谈论它，但每个人定义的它都不一样。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里存在一个常见的误解：认为只要我有了一套完美的 Evals（评估集），我就能高枕无忧地部署产品了。或者相反，认为 Evals 没用，只需要看线上监控。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">事实是，这是一个虚假的二分法。你需要明白它们各自的作用：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><strong><span leaf=\"\">1. Evals（预部署）：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;它捕获的是“已知的未知”。你基于你对产品的理解，设计测试用例来防止已知的错误模式。它是你的基准线，确保你的产品在最基本的功能上不会出错。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><strong><span leaf=\"\">2. 监控（部署后）：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;它捕获的是“未知的未知”。AI 上线后，用户一定会以你从未想象过的方式使用它。比如银行的核保系统，用户可能会突然把整个 40 页的贷款申请扔进去问“以前类似情况是怎么处理的？”，这完全超出了预设的评估范围。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“评估集只能捕捉你已经意识到的错误。而对于那些涌现式的、意想不到的行为，你必须依靠持续的校准和监控。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，不要过度迷信用大模型当裁判。在复杂的企业用例中，如果你的评估标准本身就很模糊，或者错误模式非常微妙，LLM 裁判可能根本无法捕捉。有时候，朴素的“用户反馈”和“隐式信号”（Implicit Signals，比如用户是否重新生成了答案）比复杂的代码评估更有效。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">6. AI 时代开发者最重要的核心能力</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在未来，构建本身将变得极其廉价。代码生成工具和 Agent 使得写代码不再是瓶颈。那么，开发者的核心竞争力是什么？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kiriti 提出了一个极具穿透力的观点：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“痛苦是新的护城河。”</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在没有教科书、没有标准答案的 AI 领域，成功的公司和个人，是那些愿意经历“试错痛苦”的人。你必须通过无数次的失败、调试、甚至在凌晨盯着 Agent 的错误日志，才能真正理解哪些方法行得通，哪些行不通。这种通过“痛苦”积累下来的隐性知识，是任何教程和 AI 都无法瞬间复制的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于个人开发者而言，最重要的技能将从<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“执行力”</span>转向</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“品味”、“判断力”和“设计能力”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">当实现的成本趋近于零，你选择“解决什么问题”、你如何“设计交互流程”、你如何“判断结果的好坏”，这些将成为决定成败的关键。不要再沉迷于学习每一个新出的工具，而要沉迷于你的客户和他们的问题。在 AI 时代，理解业务流程并能够重新设计它，比写出完美的 Python 代码要重要得多。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">结语：做那个“愚人”</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在访谈的最后，Aishwaria 引用了一句她父亲的话：“别人说这做不到，但那个愚人不知道，所以他做成了。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 AI 这个充满了噪音、炒作和不确定性的时代，也许我们都需要一点这种“愚人”的精神。不要被甚至专家都看不清的数据和预测吓倒。保持对问题的痴迷，保持对用户的同理心，接受构建过程中的痛苦。因为正是这些痛苦，正在为你挖掘一条通往未来的护城河。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\">内容来源：“Why most AI products fail”丨Lenny's Podcast</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频网址：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z7T1pCxgvlA&amp;t=13s\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z7T1pCxgvlA&amp;t=13s</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文总结了 OpenAI 与 Google 专家构建 50 多款 AI 产品的实战经验，提出了应对非确定性系统的 CCCD 框架，强调可靠性与信任是 AI 产品成功的核心。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文总结了 OpenAI 与 Google 专家构建 50 多款 AI 产品的实战经验，提出了应对非确定性系统的 CCCD 框架，强调可靠性与信任是 AI 产品成功的核心。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了 AI 产品失败的深层原因，指出 AI 作为概率性系统与传统确定性软件在输入输出及代理权控制上的本质区别。核心观点认为，成功的产品构建应遵循 CCCD（持续校准，持续开发）框架，提倡从低代理权的路由助手（V1）逐步演进到全自动代理（V3），以此建立用户信任并积累高质量数据。文章还强调了领导者亲身实践、解决数据债务以及建立完善监控体系的重要性，并指出在 AI 时代，开发者的核心竞争力将从单纯的代码执行转向业务品味与设计判断力。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 产品是概率性系统，面临双向非确定性挑战。",
      "explanation": "不同于传统软件的确定性逻辑，AI 产品的输入意图多样且输出结果不可控，开发者需在非确定性技术中寻求企业级的确定性结果。"
    },
    {
      "point": "代理权与控制权之间存在零和博弈。",
      "explanation": "赋予 AI 越多决策权，组织就失去越多控制权。产品初期过度追求高代理权往往会导致品牌声誉或资金安全的灾难性风险。"
    },
    {
      "point": "采用阶梯式构建方法（CCCD）来逐步建立信任。",
      "explanation": "从高控制的路由助手开始，通过 Copilot 模式收集人类纠偏数据，最后在准确率达标后再释放全自动代理权限。"
    },
    {
      "point": "可靠性是企业级 AI 产品的核心货币。",
      "explanation": "消费级产品容忍幻觉，但企业级应用的一次错误可能导致法律诉讼。保护用户体验的同时进行后台学习是建立长期信任的关键。"
    },
    {
      "point": "开发者的核心竞争力转向品味与判断力。",
      "explanation": "当代码生成变得廉价，选择解决什么问题、设计何种交互流程以及判断结果好坏的能力将成为区分优秀开发者的护城河。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "很多团队是从「模型能做什么」开始的，而不是从「用户真正需要什么」开始。",
    "每当你赋予 AI 更多的代理权（做决策的能力），你就必须放弃相应程度的控制权。",
    "即使拥有最好的模型，要在企业内部构建一个能产生显著 ROI 的系统，通常也需要 4 到 6 个月的脏活累活。",
    "不要通过牺牲用户体验来换取 AI 的学习，要在保护用户体验的同时进行后台学习。",
